data.value:
This program has been created for both students and professors. As a student or a professor you can create your own tests and generate up to 4 different versions of a test.
The goal of this program is to help students study for upcoming exam. At the same time this program is designed to help professors by minimizing the chance for cheating.
This program was created by Svetlana Marhefka in 2017. If you should have any questions or comments please feel free to e-mail me at: svetlanamarhefka@gmail.com
Thank you and I hope this program is of benefit to you.
